00:00:20.331 --> 00:00:22.791
<v ->Some of us watch old movies to be taken back to a time</v>

3
00:00:22.791 --> 00:00:24.671
when life was more gentle and simple

4
00:00:24.671 --> 00:00:26.413
and people were more direct.

5
00:00:26.413 --> 00:00:28.891
Others of us know people who, just sitting with them,

6
00:00:28.891 --> 00:00:31.491
bring grace into our lives.

7
00:00:31.491 --> 00:00:33.531
Adele Seronde is one such woman.

8
00:00:33.531 --> 00:00:35.851
Raised by a well-educated and artistic family

9
00:00:35.851 --> 00:00:37.871
who had a passion for gardening,

10
00:00:37.871 --> 00:00:40.851
Adele has spent her life dedicated to assisting humanity

11
00:00:40.851 --> 00:00:42.811
to keep our connection with the earth,

12
00:00:42.811 --> 00:00:44.251
beginning with childhood.

13
00:00:44.251 --> 00:00:46.291
She has always been an original thinker

14
00:00:46.291 --> 00:00:49.251
who insists that once we lose our connection with nature,

15
00:00:49.251 --> 00:00:51.491
we lose our connection with self.

16
00:00:51.491 --> 00:00:53.531
She keeps her connection through poetry,

17
00:00:53.531 --> 00:00:54.771
art, and gardening.

18
00:00:54.771 --> 00:00:57.071
Nearing 90 years of age, I was lucky enough

19
00:00:57.071 --> 00:00:59.711
to spend time with her in Sedona recently,

20
00:00:59.711 --> 00:01:02.011
where she has been a community and environmental activist

21
00:01:02.011 --> 00:01:05.371
for many years.

22
00:01:05.371 --> 00:01:08.451
Adele, you've written an absolutely beautiful book

23
00:01:08.451 --> 00:01:11.471
based on the own richness of your experience

24
00:01:11.471 --> 00:01:14.611
and your life, and whether you're talking about it

25
00:01:14.611 --> 00:01:17.491
literally or metaphorically, you're talking about

26
00:01:17.491 --> 00:01:20.531
each and every one of our own sacred gardens

27
00:01:20.531 --> 00:01:22.131
<v ->That's true.</v>

28
00:01:22.131 --> 00:01:23.131
<v ->which we must be responsible for participating in</v>

29
00:01:23.131 --> 00:01:26.251
