00:01:37.891 --> 00:01:41.471
this kind of elegance that existed in the 20's.

35
00:01:41.471 --> 00:01:42.971
<v ->Another time.</v>

36
00:01:42.971 --> 00:01:46.231
<v ->Another time, born into a family where your father</v>

