00:06:42.051 --> 00:06:44.551
but I felt somehow cleansed,

141
00:06:44.551 --> 00:06:46.871
and I also felt right then and there

142
00:06:46.871 --> 00:06:51.871
gardens are needed for people, needed as a means

143
00:06:51.911 --> 00:06:56.911
of not only the ideas that can be nurtured there,

144
00:06:57.171 --> 00:06:59.831
so you have gardens of the mind,

145
00:06:59.831 --> 00:07:04.671
but the physical activity, the embracing

146
00:07:04.671 --> 00:07:09.671
of all the plants, the insects of nature essentially.

147
00:07:10.391 --> 00:07:14.231
And I said, "This is available to everybody."

148
00:07:14.231 --> 00:07:16.411
The whole world can do this.

149
00:07:16.411 --> 00:07:18.231
It's not something that blows

150
00:07:18.231 --> 00:07:22.271
to the rich or the poor, can eventually come.

